Package: aactreveal
Type: Package
Title: Extract Useful AACT (clinialtrials.gov) Information 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Howard Baek [aut, cre], Thomas Jemielita [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Howard Baek <howard.baek@merck.com>
Description: This package provides various data loader and query functions to help 
    explore the AACT (Aggregate Content of ClinicalTrials.gov) database. Key functionalities 
    include: (1) Data loader functions, (2) Query treatment/condition/outcomes, 
    (3) Web-scraping to find related terms of a given treatment/condition,
    (4) Functions that generate analysis data sets for subsequent analyses.
License: GPL (>=3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.0)
Imports:
  dplyr, rvest, selectr, stringdist, stringr, xml2, readr, odbc, rlang, purrr, tidyr, pins
RoxygenNote: 7.2.2
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
